  • public class GobblinTaskStateModelFactory
extends org.apache.helix.task.TaskStateModelFactory
    A TaskStateModelFactory for GobblinTaskStateModels.

    This class is currently not used but may get used in the future if we decide to plugin our own custom TaskStateModel. So currently this is like a place holder class.
